{"tid":1418540,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一個讚美下大家係5/8既付出同貢獻丫","createTime":"2019-08-05T19:06:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T03:54:29.000Z","uid":297179,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"1d0a7c6fdcebe0ba747f6d4c0dd4feef661ce6ce","tid":1418540,"uid":297179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T19:06:40.000Z","msg":"我自己今日去左好多地方，發現到好幾個無名英雄既事跡想同大家分享下。分別係：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uNAzPSV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuNAzPSV.jpg&h=aad004b9&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n假警察Road block頂住條葵涌路（我唔太識形容個位)，D巴士佬唔識分真假，即使有人識穿左搬開左都唔敢衝，直至交通警到左清場先通返。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/c9MLb6c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fc9MLb6c.jpg&h=812d0e96&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n機場文宣組，我眼見得三個，佢哋都照做！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ExRjgBK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FExRjgBK.jpg&h=a5c062b1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有衫比有需要既人換。<br />\n<br />\n大家都辛苦了，少D怨氣，多D讚美啦。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雖然我話一人一個，我自己都發現幾個，你同你朋友都應該收埋唔少，分享下啦。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d121c8bd9a31e16173d229db1a37e49d07d45ebf","tid":1418540,"uid":297179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T19:14:46.000Z","msg":"可能大家會唔明我既出發點。正能量好緊要！<br />\n推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13404ae9ffc78dd1a74243f021687a66ba6d8b46","tid":1418